dc_description_s: These data layers represent addresses for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Shawano_Addresses_2017.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Shawano_Address_2017', 'Shawano_Driveway_2017', and 'Shawano_PrimaryStructure_2017'. [Address: Address number annotation layer. Driveway: Driveway point coverage. PrimaryStructure: Build point coverage.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
